response.original_title: Songs for the 8th Fire At Massey Hall
response.overview: Filmed just as people were permitted to gather in small groups again, this film documents artists of Ishkōdé  Records meeting in-person for the first time where they introduce themselves, connect and discuss their ambitions, and perform for each other in the round, on stage in historic Massey Hall.
response.title: Songs for the 8th Fire At Massey Hall
